{"tid":2308499,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"「內褲裡面⋯兩個字」點燃綜藝魂！　伯賢挺KAI反差萌：挖出另一面","createTime":"2020-12-02T02:43:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-02T04:54:21.000Z","uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6404b20997dcd8e3f102be0286f26eee3b7b4710","tid":2308499,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T02:43:39.000Z","msg":"南韓天團EXO繼伯賢、CHEN、SUHO、LAY之後，成員KAI也單飛出輯，成為EXO中第五位SOLO出道者。KAI為此出演多個綜藝節目，展現不同於舞台上的性感魅力，搞笑又親和的真實模樣顛覆大眾以往對於KAI的高冷印象。專輯發售當天，KAI的線上記者會，也由隊友隊員伯賢情義相挺擔任主持人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5307/d5307501.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5307%2Fd5307501.jpg&h=cadf7c13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲KAI出道8年，發行首張迷你專輯《KAI - The 1st Mini Album》。（圖／avex taiwan提供）<br />\n<br />\n對於活動8年以來的SOLO出道心情，KAI表示很激動也很緊張，此張專輯是懷抱著對粉絲感恩的心努力準備的。被問到朋友們是否有給予SOLO活動的建議，KAI表示，好友泰民提供SOLO時的注意事項、伯賢在錄音方面給予了很直接的幫助、成員們則是站在粉絲EXO-L的立場，在專輯製作上給予許多意見與創意。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5307/d5307499.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5307%2Fd5307499.jpg&h=5a5bbac3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲KAI成為EXO中第五位SOLO出道者。（圖／avex taiwan提供）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n伯賢更在旁補充說道：「KAI的聲音很有魅力。算有機會可以展現。」期待KAI通過這次的單飛而成長的樣貌，除了期待KAI的個人專輯外，也期盼再次以EXO合體時，展現出不一樣的火花。近來積極出演綜藝節目展現舞台下的樣貌，KAI說：「在EXO活動時好像給人比較強烈的印象，現在想給大家看我也有比較柔和自在的一面。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5307/d5307500.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5307%2Fd5307500.jpg&h=06757c8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲KAI出道8年，發行首張迷你專輯《KAI - The 1st Mini Album》。（圖／avex taiwan提供）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n伯賢也說，KAI其實是很有趣的人，也蠻聰明的，希望可以多挖掘出他的另一面。KAI另外也在廣播節目上提到，自從去年出演《認識的哥哥》後，在節目中因為說出「內褲裡面⋯兩個字」的橋段引爆回想，甚至成為流行語後，增加了自己出演綜藝節目的自信心。KAI首張個人迷你專輯《KAI - The 1st Mini Album》已在台數位發行。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5307/d5307498.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5307%2Fd5307498.jpg&h=96f1ba5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲KAI去年出演《認識的哥哥》，說出「內褲裡面⋯兩個字」的橋段引爆迴響。（圖／翻攝自YouTube／jtbc）"},{"pid":"088cf88f2cc01b3e731ecda361989b20edbba393","tid":2308499,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T02:48:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acf20802875764738d89bf6a896824d088963d60","tid":2308499,"uid":165368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T03:26:40.000Z","msg":"個答案係咩..<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f9363eb177bc8055ffe9689836dc23d6195e2ef","tid":2308499,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"acf20802875764738d89bf6a896824d088963d60","tid":2308499,"uid":165368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T03:26:40.000Z","msg":"個答案係咩..<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T03:30:12.000Z","msg":"巨龍？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"005ed389e7e695d00fd07c0b660d00461c679c98","tid":2308499,"uid":237818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"acf20802875764738d89bf6a896824d088963d60","tid":2308499,"uid":165368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T03:26:40.000Z","msg":"個答案係咩..<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T03:57:04.000Z","msg":"暖包"},{"pid":"6a71589e17ddd7b0ae1d404aad0b4661c25b9bf9","tid":2308499,"uid":162726,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T04:49:59.000Z","msg":"Kai子前世做咗咩好事先食到2個西女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"4bd4b8c0235b94384f01162cdd92849a7dfc8c0e","tid":2308499,"uid":143093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T04:54:21.000Z","msg"